OL,3,CDisabled people in Bristol could be
OL,4,Cmoved to care homes to save council
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FDisabled people in Bristol could be
OL,8,Fforced to live in care homes if it is
OL,9,Fcheaper than providing support for
OL,10,Fthem in their own homes.
OL,12,FBristol City Council's proposed Fair
OL,13,Fand Affordable Care Policy says
OL,14,Fdisabled people whose in-home care
OL,15,Fexceeds the local authority rates
OL,16,Fcould be placed in nursing or
OL,17,Fresidential homes under a new scheme.
OL,19,FThe policy is currently out for public
OL,20,Fconsultation until 31 January 2024.
